- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is also likely as the paper develops security guarantees for the FLAFOL logic. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possible category as the paper formalizes the FLAFOL proof system. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is another possible category as the paper deals with authorization decisions and security guarantees, which are important aspects of software engineering. 
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper presents a new logic and formalizes its proof system.
